.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
\fBVISUAL\fR, \fBEDITOR\fR
Editor used by \fBrdebootstrap edit\fR (unless \fB--edit\fR is provided).
.TP
\fBXDG_CACHE_HOME\fR
Base directory for the cache when \fB--cache-dir\fR is not set.
.TP
\fBVAULT_ADDR\fR, \fBVAULT_TOKEN\fR, \fBVAULT_CACERT\fR, \fBVAULT_SKIP_VERIFY\fR
Vault client configuration when using \fB--auth vault:<...>\fR.
